title: For Sale/Trade:  1,000 Rounds Golden Tiger 7.62x39
postcontent:
WTS/WTT a case of 1,000 rounds of the accurate, consistent, clean, highly sought after Golden Tiger. This ammo sold out across the country almost immediately following the sanctions against Russia last year. According to one of their largest importers, SG Ammo, whether or not we will receive any more is questionable, and the factory may be producing for the Russian Gov't rather than US sales because the sale price is double in Russia vs. the U.S. 

If you own a weapon chambered in 7.62x39mm, you want to have some of this in your emergency stash. The bullets are sealed at the case neck and the primers are sealed as well. The bullets are boat tailed FMJs that have an air pocket at the front end, which means they fly straight and they tumble and fragment reliably. This ammo is remarkably accurate our of my SBR. Huge difference between Golden Tiger and Wolf when it comes to consistency and accuracy. Don't take my word for it, do some research and see for yourself. 

$350 Face-to-Face in St. Petersburg or Pinellas Park only 

I'd prefer to trade for a semi auto handgun in 9mm, .40S&W, .357SIG or .45ACP. Lemme know what you've got!
